Silver for Immediate Delivery Rallies to All-Time High of $49.79 Per Ounce

-- B y   G l e n y s   S i m
-- 
2011-04-25T05:14:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/silver-for-immediate-delivery-rallies-to-all-time-high-of-49-79-per-ounce.html
Spot silver surged to a record,
gaining as much as 5.4 percent to $49.79 per ounce before
trading at $49.725 at 1:11 p.m. in  Singapore .  To contact the reporter on this story:
